snippet.textDisplay:
True love?
Does true love really exist?
I was being in relationship with someone since five years. I trusted her blindly. And last week i caught her and came to know that she was in relationship with someone else since 16 months. Knowing this all things broke my heart into so many pieces. How could someone be so rude?
If she didn't want to keep the relationship than she should have told me earlier before getting into relationship with other guy.
She made me realize that " love" is just a word ,but in reality it didn't exist. 😔😭

snippet.textDisplay: Before you go - 3 words that every human in this word should ask. Life is hard, no one ever said it would be easy. I write these words as  man with a beautiful fiancee and a beautiful son that words could not  comprehend to explain how precious they are to me. Everyone goes through a low point that may seem never ending but trust me when  I say this: time is your best friend, love yourself, love your friends, family members and anyone you encounter. Love comes from the most unpredictable places. Stay strong, there is no end, there is no giving up. I promise you will find happiness.
